\">我屌你老母</span><br />\n<br />\n屌"},{"pid":"8b0b2c0145dc097a6ad14fca0da5358bd994e185","tid":96712,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:50:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望同樣喜歡魔物之手嘅人可以幫忙表達不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208ac61d09b1d0c90b3b15cda8bb9326e2f0577c","tid":96712,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:52:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望同樣喜歡魔物之手嘅人可以幫忙表達不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有撚用咩<br />\n唉<br />\n成撚日斬新作<br />\n唔知仲有咩好睇<br />\n舊連載緊既唔睇就唔睇架啦<br />\n斬撚左新作,咩都無得睇"},{"pid":"8da362a2f92e74690f134482cc2a4f010c480e66","tid":96712,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:57:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望同樣喜歡魔物之手嘅人可以幫忙表達不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有撚用咩<br />\n唉<br />\n成撚日斬新作<br />\n唔知仲有咩好睇<br />\n舊連載緊既唔睇就唔睇架啦<br />\n斬撚左新作,咩都無得睇</blockquote><br />\n最近已經斬左好多部好作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係就黎嬲到癲......到底日本個邊發生乜事"},{"pid":"80f11030d160d12e608d6ef1ffbfb5d815c7a377","tid":96712,"uid":582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T06:02:09.000Z","msg":"呢套都斬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2154e5ceab81a8805458517c18565a1c81015271","tid":96712,"uid":36332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T06:07:04.000Z","msg":"近呢個月先發現呢套野，我覺得幾高質喎<br />\n呢幾年開始令我質疑自己睇漫畫嘅眼光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381e792aeca7139b080af08d5612cdd127ba380e","tid":96712,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T06:09:04.000Z",